file.name: inheritance.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Inheritance examples
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /inheritance:
    get:
      tags:
        - InheritanceService
      operationId: "inheritance"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "Description"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Entity4"

        "201":
          description: "Description"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Empty"
components:
  schemas:
    Entity:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          nullable: false
        name:
          type: string
          nullable: true
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
      additionalProperties: false

    Entity2:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
      properties:
        description:
          type: string
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false

    Entity3:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity2'
      properties:
        summary:
          type: string
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false

    Entity4:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity3'
      properties:
        notes:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        moreNotes:
          type: string
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false

    Empty:
      type: object
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
      allOf:
        - type: object

      additionalProperties: false

    Empty2:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Empty'
      additionalProperties: false

    Empty3:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Empty2'
      additionalProperties: false

    EmptyEntity:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
      additionalProperties: false

    Named:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Empty3'
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false

    WithList:
      type: object
      properties:
        list:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          nullable: false
        nullableList:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          nullable: true
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
      additionalProperties: false

    WithListDerived:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
      properties:
        list:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          nullable: false
        nullableList:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false

    WithListDerived2:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/WithList'
      properties:
        list2:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          nullable: false
        nullableList2:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Entity'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false

    WithListDerived3:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/WithList'
      properties:
        someString:
          type: string
          nullable: false
      additionalProperties: false

    WithListDerived4:
      type: object
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/WithListDerived'
      properties:
        someString:
          type: string
          nullable: false
      additionalProperties: false
